Chance Eau Tendre EdP - Chanel
Which Chanel is your favourite?🙋🏼‍♀️ 

This one was the very first perfume I tried and it's been on my wishlist ever since. I am so happy that I finally added it to my collection🥰. 

Note are: quince, grapefruit, jasmin, rose 

This perfume is so uplifting and in my opinion it is very hard not liking it🍊. It starts with a fruity sweet quince and grapefruit combo (don't get me wrong, yes it is sweet and fruity but still upgrown)🌹. 

During the drydown the flowers come through. Although a rose is listed, it is definitely not dominant at all☀️. 

I love the drydown of Chance Eau Tendre! It smells so fresh and clean with hints of flowers and quince and it actually has great lasting power🤍. I can still smell it on my clothes the next day🌸. 

It is a great everyday scent and can be worn all year round for any occassion🥰. 

I also love Gabrielle Essence from chanel.beauty

生まれたときの境遇は決められていて、しかも十人十色。

変えられないものを嘆かず、
自分が生まれ持った魅力を
どれだけ伸ばすことができるか。

生まれた環境に文句はあっても
今の境遇は自分の歴史。

今の自分の行動が
未来の自分を想像してゆく。

今全力になれてますか？
変わらないもののせいにしていませんか？

自分をありのままに受け入れることから、
人生の道は切り拓けます。

いつまでも生まれ持ったものに
文句を言っていても何も変わらない。

人生行動あるのみ。
輝いていきましょうよ！！

"If Chanel was the archetypal designer of the first half of the century, Karl Lagerfeld is the designer who would have to be invented, if he did not already exist, to represent late-20th-century fashion. 

"He designs with exuberance and versatility, developing collections under several labels and for varied audiences. Chameleon and prestidigitator, Lagerfeld can embrace—and command—several styles simultaneously. The client for Lagerfeld's own-label clothing may not be the client for his designs for Chanel, for Fendi, for Chloe, so autonomous are the collections. Yet none of these collections have failed to demonstrate the expertise that Lagerfeld brings to fashion as an art and a business. His significant stylistic interests include the revealed structure of the garment, the modification of historical models, the connections between fine art and fashion, the combination of the traditional restraint of the couture with the flourishes of the wildest street fashions (in a gleeful confrontation of good and bad taste), and effects that turn garments upside down or inside out. 

"Creating furs, shoes, gloves, jewelry, and clothing, Lagerfeld is the complete designer. He is also the consummate connoisseur (with a special affinity for the 18th century—thus his signature fan). Lagerfeld has modeled himself on the ideal of the 18th-century artist, though he can be considered as the ultimate contemporary fashion designer-impresario."

- Richard Martin on Karl Lagerfeld, 1992

This luxurious #texturetuesday has been a longtime coming! ⁣
⁣
As I’ve stated before, the OG 2010’s YouTube beauty gurus “raised me” in terms of my knowledge and genuine love for makeup. I could sit and watch their hauls and tutorials for hours on end, so even if it was a product that was out of reach for me to actually try, you can bet I’d at least heard of it! ⁣
⁣
Enter the granddaddy of all cream bronzers….Soleil Tan de Chanel! All the It Girls of the internet used and LOVED it, so naturally I wanted it! BUT…I wouldn’t have even known where to get it, much less been able to justify the cost to buy it back then. ⁣
⁣
Fast forward to now and chanel.beauty has reformulated and renamed the iconic bronzer AND it’s sold at ultabeauty! So you know what that means….time to cash in some points and being that baby home! ⁣
⁣
And that’s exactly what I did! The LES BEIGES Healthy Glow Bronzing Cream is now mine! ⁣
⁣
I’ve been hesitant to dig into that gorgeous, creamy swirl, but I think it’s time for me to finally give it a try! While I never tried the original formula, the research I’ve done shows that they added coconut oil to the new formula, so it is supposed to be smoother and more hydrating on dry skin, so that sounds more up my alley anyway. I will definitely let y’all know what I think after I’ve had the chance to use it for a while! ⁣
⁣
Have you used this iconic bronzer? Let me know if you have any tips/tricks for applying it! ⬇️

Last spring in Paris 🤍

If this does not sounds like a dreamy romcom movie script then I don’t know what kind you’re watching?! Sofia said that she felt someone was watching over them because after a cloudy day full of preparations, at 6pm just as she reached the top steps of Eden Roc to begin her walk down the aisle, the clouds suddenly parted. Cue angels singing!! 
She began her seven and a half minute (yes, 7.5 mins with no trips or slips!!) walk down the aisle with her dad, the legendary Lionel Richie, to “a clear glass marquee adorned with an abundance of white and cream florals by Roni Floral Design” per Vogue. Sofia said that walking down the aisle with her dad was something she always dreamed of and girl, same. As they got closer to the marquee and chuppah, Sofia heard the song she’d chosen to walk down the aisle to which was fittingly “Until I Found You” by Stephen Sanchez who Elliot had flown in to surprise her with a live rendition complete with her name sprinkled through. How sweet?! 
It was important to the couple and his family that they had a traditional Jewish ceremony since Sofia converted prior to the wedding. Although they were legally married in America in their backyard with their parents as witnesses (you know, pesky paperwork biz) they loved having the chance to share their vows privately. 
After the ceremony, and what I’m sure was a longer walk back up the aisle, it was time for cocktails, dinner and dancing with Sofia’s sister, the one and only Nicole Richie emceeing. I truly couldn’t think of a better person to keep the laughter going but maybe that’s my sentimental millennial heart! You’ve got to see some closeups and products deets from Sofia’s makeup coming up next. Total perfection!

轉機真的很累😰🥺
上回包機來美國太舒適，
終於要回家，
第一次挑戰國內線轉機
西南航空的空中bus 都沒有劃位，
只有分group ABC排隊順序，要加價的是A組，可以先排隊入座才能家人坐在一起，我爸媽上次轉機不知道要這樣，兩人還分開位置，
上飛機後找位置先到先坐～
短程才一小時很快降落
拿到大行李之後，
又要自己扛到下一個terminal ….

LA 的ONT 機場
國內線在terminal 4 要轉到terminal 2 
搭乘shuttle bus才會到國際線… 安檢又重新來一次， 這段最累😞

好險Coco精力旺盛👍
從頭到尾都自己推登機箱
非常乖的跟著大人走～
而且沒有什麼吵鬧，
唯一唉唉叫一次是超過晚上8點還沒吃晚餐，
後來也是忍耐到VIP lounge 
才吃一點麵線和點心，
一上飛機就起飛秒睡
真的好開心😀

不過有些想念家門口春天不同顏色的花朵～才剛開始綻放🌹
又要等一年後才看得到了～

🌷As a business owner, lessons on her leadership hold a dynamic approach to how we must conduct our business. 

🌷Queen Elizabeth understood that her platform was as a visionary. 

🌷Her platform was not focused on immediate gratification, yet it was positioned to weather volatility. 

🌷Her Majesty understood the power of playing the long game.

Die einzigartige Geschichte von Louis Vuitton begann im Jahr 1837. Damals machte sich der 16-Jährige Louis Vuitton auf den Weg nach Paris. Dort absolvierte er eine Ausbildung zum Kofferhersteller.

1854 entschloss sich Louis Vuitton dazu, seine eigene Werkstatt zu eröffnen. Diese eröffnete er unter dem Namen „Louis Vuitton Malletier“ in Paris, als Kofferhersteller.

Zusammen mit seinem Sohn Georges entwickelte Louis Vuitton im Jahr 1886 das revolutionäre Tumbler Schloss. Mit diesem Schloss Verwandelten sie ihre Koffer in wahre Schatztruhen.

Bis heute sind diese wundervollen Reisekoffer ein einzigartiger Erfolg. Lassen Sie sich von einem großen Sortiment an Louis Vuitton Reisegepäck bei As Luxury in der Sophienstraße 15 in Baden-Baden begeistern. Wir freuen uns auf Ihre Anfrage, auch gerne über unseren Versand.

前幾年在陳姐與戶長領進門之下，
除了開啟萬劫不復的精品路(?)，
自己莫名奇妙踏進去的𝐕𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐞坑，
更是讓我不(荷)見(包)天(破)日(洞)( ᐛ )」

每一次逛𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐞都感覺是在逛博物館，
一不小心就收了各種絲巾、飾品(˶‾᷄ ⁻̫ ‾᷅˵)
而最喜歡的，莫過於這顆𝐊𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐲包了♡
當知道它已經超過自己的歲數，
並且被小心翼翼、完好如初地保存至今時，
那種心情跟去專櫃的感覺又大不相同.ᐟ.ᐟ
雖然收到的第一天就不小心刮傷它 ( •̣̣̣̣̣̥́௰•̣̣̣̣̣̥̀ )
但轉念一想，它要陪我走過漫長歲月，
所有的痕跡都是屬於我的人生記號♡
朋朋們對𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐞又是怎麼想的呢？

這次選擇了以比較輕鬆的方式詮釋毛呢，
製成了襯衫外套版型的毛呢上衣，
透過調整領口露膚的面積讓正式感減少，
拼色的設計感西裝褲也帶著幾分都會休閒感；
而這套的小心機是𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐤𝐞𝐫.ᐟ.ᐟ
去年𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐥聖誕限定的緞帶實在太可愛了，
看了各種𝐃𝐈𝐘後，索性決定當成𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐤𝐞𝐫♡
自己覺得這套相較於其他毛呢𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐟𝐢𝐭，
比較帶有個性與休閒的感覺(◍•ᴗ•◍)

Selbstverständlich sind verschiedene Chanel Accessoires, Schmuck und Damenhandtaschen insbesondere auch von einer der berühmtesten Taschen der Welt bei AS Luxury erhältlich:

Die Chanel Timeless oder auch 2.55 bezeichnet.

Die “2.55” von Chanel ist nicht nur eine der weltweit bekanntesten Taschen, sie ist auch die Mutter aller Schultertaschen für Damen: Mit diesem Modell - benannt nach dem Datum ihrer Entstehung im Februar 1955 – schenkte Designerin Gabrielle Chanel den Frauen ein bisschen mehr Freiheit im Alltag. Inspiriert von Militärgepäck, entwarf Chanel eine edle Handtasche mit Trageriemen, so dass diese erstmals über die Schulter gehängt werden konnte und die Hände frei waren.

🇬🇧老倫敦CHANEL Vintage初體驗🇬🇧
「美包不等人！只等那位有。緣。人。🎉🛎️🛎️🛎️🎉」
老倫敦直播中買包才有的福利口號⋯我自己喊一下🤣
之前因為疫情不開放門市或是行程不湊巧，大概錯過了3次老倫敦，這次保持著朝聖的心情，終於首次踏入了老倫敦的大門🎉原本只是想進去逛逛參觀而已，也許有喜歡的小飾品意思意思收一下就好，雖然有在看老倫敦的直播，但現場聽到胸針、項鍊都要5～6萬起跳，還是忍不住倒抽一口氣😳（畢竟都鍍K金！）店員領著我參觀精緻又充滿驚喜的門市，在店裡的體驗完全是VIC般的禮遇，服務非常週到又熱情，完全值得給予5星評價的老香聖地🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟
逛了一會之後他說：「等我一下⋯有一個包很適合你！」然後端出了這顆✨CF Jumbo✨ （aka.貝嫂包）1996-1997年份近27歲的包款，但是狀況超好，根本凍齡啊！超澎的小羊皮+黃澄澄的鍍24K金+皮穿鏈可側背、肩背、手提多功能！我眼睛早已離不開它了😍 不要問多少錢（俗氣🤣）
Vintage會因為成色、質料還有整體狀況各種原因價差很大，也不見得高價就買得到一模一樣的品質，總之20萬有找，Vintage的緣分也是可遇不可求，也許上帝覺得我有認真練復活節吧⋯給了一個如此超乎所求所想的獎勵❤️

Aura Flora by Sally-Ann Provan Millinery ✨

Twenty-two milliners from the britishhatguild have collaborated with thejockeyclub and braintumoursch, creating headpieces in the colours of King Charles' racing silks. These pieces are being auctioned online to raise funds for Brain Tumour Research.

Aura Flora takes its name and inspiration from a loose Latin translation of “golden flowers”. The piece was moulded or ‘blocked’ by hand, using steam over a wooden block made by one of the last hat-block makers working in the UK. It is made from sinamay which is a straw material made from abaca, a member of the banana plant family growing in the Philippines and the gold sheen on the handmade silk and leather flowers is 23.5ct gold leaf, applied by hand.
 
Made with a sinamay base and decorated with gold silk and leather handmade origami flowers, with gold leaf applied and finished with black open work wire leaves, adorned with gold Swarovski crystal pearls, the piece is designed to be worn on the right.

Worn here with the 1950s raw silk ivory dress with statement bow to front by Stephanie Jane (Made in England) Available to shop now via the website ✨

ESP-Sofia Richie a destronado a Hailey y se convierte en la nueva It Girl y también en el nuevo ícono del estilo old money. Con outfits minimalistas y con toques más arriesgados.
Creo que es la mejor evolución de estilo. Antes tenían un estilo más callejero y en los últimos años a encontrado su estilo, pero también de vez en cuando la vemos usar prendas más arriesgadas. 
Y sin ninguna duda se ha convertido en un ícono para la casa Chanel. 

La semana de su boda a demostrado su cambio de estilo, con unos looks muy old money y casi todos de de Chanel. 

Los vestidos de boda también por obra de Chanel, demuestran elegancia y sencillez pero no pasan por desapercibidos. 

ENG- Sofia Richie has dethroned Hailey and has become the new It Girl and also the new icon of old money style. With minimalist outfits and more daring touches.
I think it's the best style evolution. Before she had a more street style and in the last few years she has found her style, but also from time to time we see her wearing more risky outfits. 
And without any doubt she has become an icon for Chanel. 

The week of her wedding showed her change of style, with some very old money looks and almost all from Chanel. 

The wedding dresses also by Chanel, show elegance and simplicity but do not go unnoticed.

Did I mention seeing Timothée in NY is such a comfort? Because it’s worth repeating.❤️

On March 9, Meghan marked International Women's Day through a visit to Harvest Home, a Los Angeles charity which supports expecting mothers & their children. Along with members of the Archewell team, Meghan helped put together a baby boutique for the organization, and was seen out to lunch in LA the same day. 

For this event, the duchess chose a monochrome separates look, including a black cashmere coat by maxmara, a matching ribbed sweater possibly by the same brand, and altuzarra cropped trousers. She accessorized with her maisonvalentino sunglasses & flats, as well as a new chanelofficial statement bag which we haven't seen her carry before. For jewelry, she wore some large, possibly vintage enamel button earrings, a UFO gold necklace, and her usual bracelet stack including her cartier watch & bentleyskinner diamond bracelet.

I really loved this look on Meghan. For me an all-black look will always be the height of chic, although this one was obviously worn in LA it gives me New York or Paris style vibes. I think that's why I like it so much - while simple, this is a super versatile look that would work well for so many different occasions or locations. Personally I find that Meghan does these sort of "upscale casual" or borderline on/off-duty looks very well (I've included a few examples on the last slide here!). 

The cropped trouser/pointed flat is a vintage-esque feature that I always love, and as usual for me Meghan's accessorizing was pretty on point here - as a flats girl myself I love the shoes, and I'm pretty much always on board for a statement bag. The only part of the outfit I didn't like were the earrings. These seemed a little too large & out of place with the rest of the look for me - I think I would have opted for a small gold hoop or stud instead. But overall, it was a hit for me! What did you think? 🖤

Коко Шанель часть 1️⃣
 
Коко Шанель ( настоящее имя Габриель) намеренно окутала свою жизнь тайной. Понять ее одежду проше, чем ее саму.
 
В годы 1 Мировой Войны имя Шанель стало известным благодаря революционной простоте ее нарядов. В созданных Коко моделях прослеживается спортивный дух - мужская одежда для женщин. 
 
Шанель пренебрегала классовыми различиями  и одевала богатых дам в полосатые тельняшки как у бедных моряков. 
 
Коко любила бижутерию и  носила ее чуть ли не больше, чем настоящие драгоценности, которых у нее было предостаточно. 
 
Она изобрела свой тип универсальной вещи- маленькое черное платье, которое было настолько простым, что подходило на все случаи жизни.

Attention to the DETAILS is what makes the difference between BLABBERING and NARRATING.
°
I've said it before, and I am not going to get tired of repeating it, as it is quintessential to understanding and forming an adequate picture of what I am talking about, WORDS alone are certainly not enough to create a STORYTELLER.
°
But, before I move forward, let me once again make one premise clear enough, so that I try and reduce the possibilities of being misinterpreted by potential newcomers, suddenly dropping here and stumbling upon our today's rendezvous for an unexpected glitch in Instagram's well-calculated algorithms.
°
Whenever I mention STORYTELLING in this context, and whenever I use a terminology that overtly refers to a VERBAL METAPHOR, feel comfortable by replacing that seemingly unidirectional nomenclature with the one that best describes what NARRATION is all about for what you're currently exploring.
°
So, WORDS can easily become COLORS, SOUNDS, TEXTURES, and even TASTES and AROMAS, depending on the angle of observation you are looking at the phenomenon of SELF-EXPRESSION from.
°
When we're just CHATTING, unless we're maliciously and manipulatively trying to accomplish some evolutionarily meaningless and even self-damaging goal, DETAILS can be overlooked, without affecting the overall triviality of what we're trying to convey.
°
But we don't need to refer to high-flown literature to see how this idea, and, of course, its masterful implementation, has the mind-blowing power of transforming whatever it touches, from embarrassing to astonishing.
°
Just ask a starred gourmet chef what happens if you start pouring salt, and all sort of spices, RANDOMLY and without a genuine GUSTATORY and OLFACTORY reason.
°

..Olierollers..

•Super fijn ter ondersteuning van vanalles en nog wat! Een olieroller bevat een kogelballetje waardoor aanbrengen heel eenvoudig is. Breng ze aan op de pulse punten (te zien op afbeelding 1) zodat de oliën direct hun werk kunnen doen. Pulse punten zijn de plekken waar je de hartslag kan voelen en waar de oliën snel op alle plekken komt waar ze nodig zijn. 

•Deze manier van aanbrengen heeft een directe werking. Zo ook het aanbrengen van de (verdunde) etherische oliën onder de voeten. Onze voeten bevatten namelijk zo'n 72.000 zenuwuiteinden! Hier wordt bijvoorbeeld ook gebruik van gemaakt met voetreflexmassage/therapie. Wanneer je (verdunde) etherische oliën onder de voet aanbrengt kun je je voorstellen dat deze supersnel in de cellen van je lichaam terechtkomen. Ook heel fijn wanneer je een olie specifiek gebruikt voor zijn werking en de geur niet zo waardeert 😁

•Topisch gebruik. Het direct aanbrengen op de plek waar het nodig is. Ook hier zijn de rollers super handig voor! Denk bijvoorbeeld aan een roller met een mix voor de beschadigde huid of pijnlijke spieren. Of een roller met een mix om littekens te verminderen. 

•Olierollers kunnen ook ingezet worden puur voor de geur. Om de emoties te beïnvloeden, bijvoorbeeld met een roller met ontspannende geuren wanneer er stress heerst. Maar ook gewoon als parfum. Ook hier is het aanbrengen op de pulse punten een mooi uitgangspunt. De warmere plekjes van je lichaam. Ik citeer: 'Breng parfum aan op de plekken waar je gekust wilt worden ' - Gabrielle Chanel. 😉 Hoe tof is het dat deze ook nog eens je gemoedstoestand kunnen beïnvloeden. 

•Zoals je kunt lezen.. Multi inzetbaar!

【 girlstyle.sg 】 Chanel Has New Heart-Shaped Purses + Mini Bag With Heart-Shaped Clasp & Luxe Quilted Texture
.
Chanel’s Spring-Summer 2023 collection has recently dropped in Singapore and among the extensive range of stylish  new handbags and shoes, what caught our eye were a couple of love-themed leather purses. Either shaped like hearts, or with little heart-shaped details, these chic accessories with a quilted texture will add a fine feminine touch to any getup.
.
Made from lambskin, this pristine white Chanel Wallet On Chain will be your best friend if you’re someone who likes heading out with just your phone, cash, and cards, but hates the lack of freedom that comes with constantly clutching your items in your hands. Essentially a mini bag, this minimalistic piece’s defining feature is an enamel heart-shaped clasp.
.
In contrast, the fabric on the interior of the purse is striking red. Aside from the main inner compartment is a zippered portion and multiple card slots.
.
Cute, yet bearing a certain timelessness, is this heart-shaped Chanel Clutch With Chain in shiny black patent leather. It comes with a smaller white "baby" version of itself which you can either use on its own, or have it clipped onto other bags as an oversized keychain cum easy-access purse.
.
If you don’t quite fancy the black patent clutch but find yourself eyeing the little Zippered Coin Purse that comes along with it, you can always purchase it as a standalone item.
.

✨ SUBLIMAGE LE CORRECTEUR YEUX de chanel.beauty 

🤍Corrector de alta cobertura ideal para pieles maduras que contiene el famoso tratamiento de Chanel de su línea Sublimage.

✨Desde que salió hace unos meses tenía muchos deseos de probarlo y ahora que llegó a Perú no dude en hacerme con él. 

🤍Mi área más problemática son mis ojeras ya que tengo hiperpigmentación, piel sensible y extremadamente seca. He probado múltiples correctores tanto de alta gama como low cost sin encontrar alguno con el que me haya “casado” el que más me ayudó por varios años fue el Shape tape de Tarte del cual gasté 5 frascos (fue el único que use por varios años) pero a pesar de que me cubría muy bien y me duraba todo el día al pasar los años y mi piel madurar ya no me favorecía y su versión hidratante no me convenció.  Desde hace un año y medio aproximadamente el born this way de too faced es el que venía usando como corrector aunque me gusta más como base para todo el rostro sobre todo cuando debo estar en auditorios o virtualmente dictando conferencias y Charlas. 

✨Este corrector de Chanel se hizo viral, ha sido altamente recomendado por varias de las creadoras de contenido que sigo así que mis expectativas son MUY ALTAS (Siendo realista que tampoco hará magia 🫣) 

Lo usé por primera vez ayer que estuve en cámara y la verdad me encantó el resultado ➡️en la segunda foto podrás ver cómo luce (foto sin filtro) el empaque no me gusta para nada ya que se desperdicia producto y por ese precio quiero que me dure toda la vida 😝 la brocha que trae es de buena calidad e ideal para difuminarlo. 

✨Pronto les muestro en un Reel el antes y después de aplicarlo 🤍

En Perú lo pueden adquirir en perfumeriasunidasperu  y si están en Lima les recomiendo altamente la tienda ubicada en el Real Plaza Salaverry, allí pueden preguntar por Mariela quien las va a atender y asesorar de la mejor manera.

Eines unserer Highlights: Die Kelly Bag in einem ikonischen Gelbton. Absolut außergewöhnlich.

Genießen Sie die interessante und fein selektierte Auswahl an Kelly Bags von Hermès bei AS Luxury in der Sophienstraße 15 in Baden-Baden, oder gerne beantworten wir Ihre Anfragen auch zu unserem Versand.

“Der Traum einer jeden Frau", so beschreibt die Zeitschrift Gala diese wunderschöne Tasche.

Oft beträgt die Wartezeit für eine Kelly Bag bei Neubestellung viele Monate.

Hier noch eine weitere kleine Geschichte über die Kelly Bag:

Es wurde zunächst kein passender Name für die Tasche gefunden, die Entscheidung zog sich hin.

Bis Grace Kelly, als international gefeierter Hollywoodstar, ihre Version der Hermès-Tasche vor ihrem kleinen Bäuchlein hielt, um so die ersten Anzeichen ihrer Schwangerschaft zu verbergen. Ein Foto davon machte Furore und ging um die ganze Welt. Die Tasche erhielt Kultstatus. Von nun an wird die Tasche "Kelly Bag" genannt.

Eines unserer Highlights: Die Kelly Bag in einem ikonischen Gelbton. Absolut außergewöhnlich.

Genießen Sie die interessante und fein selektierte Auswahl an Kelly Bags von Hermès bei AS Luxury in der Sophienstraße 15 in Baden-Baden, oder gerne beantworten wir Ihre Anfragen auch zu unserem Versand.

“Der Traum einer jeden Frau", so beschreibt die Zeitschrift Gala diese wunderschöne Tasche.

Oft beträgt die Wartezeit für eine Kelly Bag bei Neubestellung viele Monate.

Hier noch eine weitere kleine Geschichte über die Kelly Bag:

Es wurde zunächst kein passender Name für die Tasche gefunden, die Entscheidung zog sich hin.

Bis Grace Kelly, als international gefeierter Hollywoodstar, ihre Version der Hermès-Tasche vor ihrem kleinen Bäuchlein hielt, um so die ersten Anzeichen ihrer Schwangerschaft zu verbergen. Ein Foto davon machte Furore und ging um die ganze Welt. Die Tasche erhielt Kultstatus. Von nun an wird die Tasche "Kelly Bag" genannt.

Eines unserer Highlights: Die Kelly Bag in einem ikonischen Gelbton. Absolut außergewöhnlich.

Genießen Sie die interessante und fein selektierte Auswahl an Kelly Bags von Hermès bei AS Luxury in der Sophienstraße 15 in Baden-Baden, oder gerne beantworten wir Ihre Anfragen auch zu unserem Versand.

“Der Traum einer jeden Frau", so beschreibt die Zeitschrift Gala diese wunderschöne Tasche.

Oft beträgt die Wartezeit für eine Kelly Bag bei Neubestellung viele Monate.

Hier noch eine weitere kleine Geschichte über die Kelly Bag:

Es wurde zunächst kein passender Name für die Tasche gefunden, die Entscheidung zog sich hin.

Bis Grace Kelly, als international gefeierter Hollywoodstar, ihre Version der Hermès-Tasche vor ihrem kleinen Bäuchlein hielt, um so die ersten Anzeichen ihrer Schwangerschaft zu verbergen. Ein Foto davon machte Furore und ging um die ganze Welt. Die Tasche erhielt Kultstatus. Von nun an wird die Tasche "Kelly Bag" genannt.

Bleu De Chanel Parfum by Chanel is a 5 star flanker in the BDC lineup, I was a fan of the EDP but the Parfum just hits different, that's more to my liking. It's spicer and on my skin the performance and longevity is second to none from the others. When BDC parfum wafts in the air you're still getting the homage of the bdc dna but with this added POWER... With the parfum I'm getting a more woodsy take on the already great dna. 

If you're someone who really enjoys each offering of the EDT for its more lighter playfulness creation or if youre someone who enjoys the EDP for its little more serious approach with added depth you'll be in love as you  get the best of both worlds in this DNA with the added sandlewood  and an ambery dry down thats captivating. 

Performance: 8.5/10
Longevity: 8.25/10

During his tenure at #Chanel, Galantic was credited with championing local artistic direction and arts and culture initiatives that elevated the brand’s image. He also launched the U.S. #ecommerce platforms, which paved the way for a global Chanel.com site, as well as the first Client app, extending one-on-one luxury service beyond the boutique.

Galantic first joined Chanel in 2006 and took on an additional #global leadership role in 2017 to establish the Integrated Platform team, which was later renamed Global Digital Services. Under his leadership, #Chanel transformed into a powerhouse, pioneering a client-centric model that increased the brand’s owned distribution and elevated the client experience.

As the news of Galantic’s resignation was revealed internally, colleagues and #industry insiders expressed their gratitude for his significant contributions and the quality of the teams he built in the U.S. and #Paris. His departure marks the end of an era for Chanel, but the company remains optimistic about its future under new #leadership. O Met Gala não é apenas um tapete vermelho: é um prelúdio para uma exposição de moda anual do Metropolitan Museum of Art em Nova Iorque. É recorrente que tais exposições sejam homenagens a estilistas de renome e, em 2023, é o caso de Karl Lagerfeld com a mostra “A Line of Beauty”, cujo tapete vermelho está marcado para o dia 1 de maio. 
Karl ficou famoso pelo seu trabalho de 4 décadas na Chanel, embora tenha passado também por Fendi, Chloé e Patou. Seus designs marcantes são ainda relevantes até mesmo após a sua morte em 2019 após sua luta contra um câncer pancreático. 
A exposição do Met homenageia seu legado de quase 70 anos de carreira contando com aproximadamente 150 peças no museu.

«La moda riflette ciò che è nell’aria. Riflette ciò che la gente legge, pensa, ascolta. E l’architettura, la pittura, i comportamenti, la società tutta», disse una volta Mary Quant, l’inventrice della minigonna ❤️‍🔥 La stilista è venuta a mancare pochi giorni fa all’età di 93 anni, ma quello che ha lasciato al mondo della moda non verrà mai dimenticato.⁠
⁠
La minigonna è fin da subito stata il capo simbolo di emancipazione femminile: le gambe scoperte sono state segno di sensualità e libertà in un’epoca a dir poco rivoluzionaria. Criticata in quanto non conforme alle regole della società dell'epoca, le donne cominciarono a indossarla rendendola il capo essenziale nel proprio armadio. Anche le passerelle dei più noti brand di moda contribuirono alla sua diffusione: chanelofficial, versace e ysl ne sono un esempio. ⁠
⁠
Ad oggi, declinata in molteplici versioni e modelli, resta senza dubbio uno tra i capi più amati in assoluto.⁠
⁠

ツヤが肌に溶け込み、もとから美しいキメの細かい素肌のように仕上げます。
厳選の保湿成分がたっぷり配合されたジェルベースで、余分な水分が揮発するときにカラー ピグメントと保湿成分が肌に密着して潤いと心地よさをキープ。

◆画像6枚目
「レ ベージュ ヘルシー グロウ イルミネーティング オイル」（50ml ￥8,580税込・限定）
潤いとツヤをプラスするヘア＆ボディオイル。繊細なゴールド パールが煌めき、髪と肌にヘルシーな輝きをもたらします。フルーティ フローラルの香りに気分もアップ！
 
◆画像7、8枚目
「ルージュ ココ フラッシュ」（2色（うち限定1色） 各￥5,500税込）

Quick Case Study: Louis Vuitton

Louis Vuitton was founded in 1854 in Paris, France, as a luggage company specializing in travel trunks.

The brand's signature monogram canvas was created in 1896 by Louis Vuitton's son, Georges. It features the LV logo and quatrefoil flower symbols and has become one of the most recognizable patterns in the fashion world.

The iconic Speedy bag was created in 1930 as a smaller version of the Keepall travel bag. It quickly became a fashion icon and has been worn by many celebrities, including Audrey Hepburn and Jessica Simpson.

Louis Vuitton is known for its collaborations with artists and designers. In 2001, the brand collaborated with Japanese artist Takashi Murakami to create the iconic Multicolore Monogram collection.

The brand's Neverfull tote bag is another iconic piece that has been popular since its introduction in 2007. Its spacious interior and stylish design have made it a favourite among fashionistas and celebrities alike.

Louis Vuitton is one of the most counterfeited luxury brands in the world. To combat this, the brand uses various anti-counterfeiting measures, such as adding holographic tags and embedding microchips in its products.

The Louis Vuitton Alma bag is another iconic piece that has been popular since its introduction in the 1930s. It was originally designed for Coco Chanel, who requested a smaller version of the brand's iconic travel trunks.

LV has a rich history of creating custom trunks for celebrities and royalty. Some of the most notable clients include Queen Elizabeth II, Muhammad Ali, and Michael Jackson.

The brand's runway shows are known for their elaborate sets and avant-garde designs. In 2012, the brand's Spring/Summer collection was shown on a giant carousel at the Louvre Museum in Paris.

Louis Vuitton has expanded beyond fashion and now offers a range of products, including jewellery, watches, and perfumes.

There’s a real beauty in balance. 

Growing up I had a few bottles of fragrance that I had gotten for Christmas and Birthdays and such, but a majority of the time I relied on my dad’s collection and sprayed from it regularly. Fast forward to when I was just getting ready to move out of state and away from home following Community College, one day I was window shopping and came across this then, fairly new release called Allure Homme by Chanel. I fell in love with that fragrance. That day I ended up buying it, my first bottle of perfume ever. I love it so much. I lost track of how bottles I’ve gone through. 

I had never smelled anything like it and haven’t since. In my opinion it’s perfect. At least it’s perfect for me. It’s perfect in Spring, it’s perfect in Summer, it’s perfect in Fall and Winter. It works brilliantly during the day, is ideal for the office, shines at night and like the title states it’s alluring in those date night situations. 

This isn’t overly bright, but has a Rich Juiciness that gets topped with a gorgeous Aldehydic Sparkle. It has a Soft, Smooth Creaminess that’s backed by a Light, but Solid Woodiness. There’s a fine grit Spice that’s paralleled by a velvety texture. And finally it has a beautiful Muskiness that’s in the mix. This is impeccably blended and all of these elements are active and play harmoniously with one another. It’s the best balanced fragrances that I’ve experienced. This fragrance makes me feel excited, ready for anything, yet calm and confident, where I’m able to be still and drink in the moment. 

I know that this is less of a review and more me just raving about something I love, but this is hands down my all-time favorite fragrance. I know that much of that for me is probably associated with memories. As you could probably tell this was more or less a signature scent for me during the part of my life when anything was possible. But, I do think that I’d be able to smell this today and still be as big of a fan of it. I don’t think I’ve ever used the word Masterpiece, but for me to date this would be the one and only Masterpiece.

If you could only label one fragrance as a masterpiece which one would it be?

【自己紹介　シャネルが好きです】
２０歳くらいからシャネルが好きです。

パイオニア（開拓者）、好きなのです。フロンティアへ切り込むのが好きなので、過渡期の混乱状態も好きです。

ココ・シャネルは、働く女性の服を作った女性の嚆矢（こうし）。下着のジャージを上着にしたり、怪我した戦士のために考案された（前開きセーターである）カーディガンのデザインをスーツに取り入れたり、斬新な考えをズバズバ実行するのがかっこいいです。動きやすく上品な服、やまとなでしこにもふさわしい服装だと思います。

さて、ココ・シャネルは、さておき。
シャネルの口紅、成人式で着物にハマった私に、母の友人が勧めました。着物に負けない存在感、鮮やかな赤。
バブルの頃と違って、穏やかな色合いが好まれますが。でも着物を着るときは、普段着であってもハレ（※）を意識して、着物に負けない顔にしたいです。

マスク生活で、マスクに色移りしないリップが重用されましたが、もうそろそろ鮮やかな色を楽しみたいのです。
で、買っちゃいました。

鮮やかに着物を楽しみます。
応援、よろしくお願いします。

※ハレは非日常、ケは日常を意味する言葉です。

Quelques mots sur la marque : 

MAEVY est une marque française créée en 2013, au style fort et original. Les vêtements et accessoires sont intégralement produits en Europe. Les modèles sont faciles à porter et à mixer et existent dans une grande gamme de couleurs. 

MAEVY utilise des matières premières d’origines animales et végétales naturelles de qualité. Leur récolte et leur transformation répondent à des contrôles fréquents et réguliers, ainsi qu’à des certifications strictes veillant au respect du bien-être des animaux et de l’environnement. 
Les fils utilisés pour la confection des mailles sont italiens, sélectionnés auprès des plus beaux filateurs. 
La marque a fait le choix de ne pas utiliser de cuir, à cause de l’impact environnemental du tannage des peaux et par respect de la vie animale. Elle crée donc des pièces dans un matériau vegan à l’aspect similaire. Dont le fameux PANTAVEGAN que je porte ici.

💞💐 I thought I'd share a few ideas for Mother's Day 🎁  in the form of a video of gifts & recent purchases from Dior, Loewe, Fendi and Louis Vuitton.
🕶💎 I adore accessories especially brooches and eyewear. I feel accessories are a great way to upgrade or transform any attire from business to casual to semi- formal etc. I stay away from "fads & Seasonal pieces" I try to buy items that I consider timeless or will become timeless pieces. 
📿 I am definitely a "Pearl Girl, haaa "Girl with Pearl Earring"#johannesvermeer 😉. I try to add brooches from every brand to my collection. I have been wanting the Loewe "Anagram brooch" but wasn't sure if I wanted it in Palladium/Multicolor, which is combination of gold, rose gold, palladium and rhodium finish. But I decided on Silver (shipped from SPAIN) & thought the Fendi small hoop earrings paired well with the brooch.
💚 I like hoop earrings but prefer studs. Just as I prefer white gold, silver, yellow gold and then Rose gold. I stay away from "Rose Gold" FASHION jewelry because I find that regardless of the brand, it tarnishes.
 💞 I had the LV "Louise Hoops earrings in GM" BUT they were just TOO heavy for me so I gifted them away & got the Louise Hoops in Mini (not shown). Now I will say that the "F Is Fendi small hoop earrings" feels about the same as the LV mini hoops but the Dior "30 Montaigne hoop earrings" are around the same size as both BUT feels the lightest on my ears. I have included pictures which shows the actual sizes along with "F Is Fendi" with a white pearl Earrings next different coins for comparison (I didn't realize how small they are). 
💞💗💞
All the brands have nice packaging with ribbons & personal notes BUT there is something a little extra about the Dior packaging, that I think is very pretty and feminine ESPECIALLY their Mother's Day design boxes (SHOWN IN VIDEO my mom's🎁). AND they give FULL SIZE SAMPLES... CONTINUED IN CAPTION
